Anatomy of a port

To get a feeling about the anatomy of a port, we will look at an example.

net/wget/
|-- Makefile
|-- distinfo
|-- patches/
|   |-- patch-configure
|   |-- patch-doc_Makefile_in
|   `-- patch-doc_wget_texi
`-- pkg/
    |-- DESCR
    `-- PLIST


